this is a telegram bot that can read&recode messages from telegram group
this bot react as my assistant in a telegram group
this bot can send all the group messages to Gemini AI for processing
this bot have 3 functions:
1. send a group histroy messages to Gemini AI and asking about a background information of this group
2. send a group histroy messages by end of the day to Gemini AI, and find out if there is any action item should be done by me
3. according to the last message in the group, suggest what should be reply in the group by using Gemini AI
